# Comparison Table

| Feature    | `==`                       | `is`                                               |
| ---------- | -------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| Compares   | Values                     | Object identity                                    |
| Returns    | `True` if values are equal | `True` if both references point to the same object |
| Used For   | Value comparison           | Identity comparison                                |
| Common Use | Numbers, strings, lists    | `None`, object identity                            |

